query:
UPDATE mods m
            SET components = jsonb_set(
                coalesce(m.components, '{}'::jsonb),
                '{minecraft_java_server_ping}',
                v.ping_data
            )
            FROM (
                SELECT
                    unnest($1::bigint[]) AS project_id,
                    unnest($2::jsonb[]) AS ping_data
            ) v
            WHERE m.id = v.project_id
